creator: GameO2
descriptionHtml:
Princess Coloring Book is a Coloring Pages Game. The user can use his fingers or light pen to color on the tactile screen of his tablet or smart-phone. has a wide gallery where there can be chosen a great quantity of images to color.

Princess Coloring Book can be one of the best educational games for the user so simultaneously that they draw amuse themselves.

Features :
- A simple palette of colors to choose the suitable color.
- To safe the drawing in the phone.
- Always you will be able to erase any color that you do not like.

DISCLAIMER
All images used in this app are believed to be in public domain.
If you own rights to any of the images, and do not wish them to appear here, please contact us and they will be removed it from the application.
descriptionShort: The Princess Coloring Book is a Coloring Pages Game.

title: Princess Coloring Pages.

descriptionHtml:
Princess Coloring Book is a Coloring Pages Game. The user can use his fingers or light pen to color on the tactile screen of his tablet or smart-phone. has a wide gallery where there can be chosen a great quantity of images to color.

Princess Coloring Book can be one of the best educational games for the user so simultaneously that they draw amuse themselves.

Features :
- A simple palette of colors to choose the suitable color.
- To safe the drawing in the phone.
- Always you will be able to erase any color that you do not like.
